---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/sections/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Disclaimer & Privacy Policy | The Riviera by Axon Developers">
  <Header />

  <main class="section section--cream policy-page">
    <div class="section-inner policy-page__inner">
      <h1 class="section-title">Disclaimer &amp; Privacy Policy</h1>

      <h2 class="policy-page__heading">Disclaimer</h2>
      <p class="section-body">
        All the content, images and logos of partners presented on this
        brochure are solely representative in nature. The images presented
        on the brochure include stock images, photographs, and artist's
        impressions to depict the property's specifications, interiors,
        exteriors, amenities, landscaping, accessibility, and other details.
        The products, fittings, finishes, and details used in the images
        are for illustrative purposes only and should not be regarded as
        standard features that are provided with the said property. A
        variation in specification during the development of a project may
        occur without prior notice. This brochure or any printed material is
        not to be construed as an offer, contract or agreement between the
        Promoter or Agent and the recipient. No booking, sale or allotment
        shall be made based on the information presented in this brochure or
        any electronic / printed material. The company will not be held
        responsible in any manner or liable for any claim of cancellation
        citing misrepresentation of information presented in this brochure.
        Readers are advised to use their discretion and verify the accuracy
        of all the details, plans, specifications, amenities, services,
        payment schedules, terms of sale, and other relevant details with
        the sales team before making the decision to buy a property.
      </p>

      <h2 class="policy-page__heading">Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p class="section-body">
        In our endeavor and commitment of protecting your personal
        information, we have designed this comprehensive privacy policy.
        This is to keep your interests and information safe on our website.
      </p>

      <h3 class="policy-page__subheading">Updation of privacy policy</h3>
      <p class="section-body">
        This privacy policy is subject to undergo change and review without
        any prior notice or approval. So to keep yourself updated on the
        changes introduced, please keep visiting and reviewing the terms and
        conditions of this privacy policy.
      </p>

      <h3 class="policy-page__subheading">User information</h3>
      <p class="section-body">
        By using our website, you agree to abide by the rules laid out by us
        and consent to collection and use of all such information that you
        may furnish to, or through, our website. In some cases, while you
        visit our website, you may not need to provide any personal
        information. But in certain instances, we must have your personal
        information in order for us to grant you access to some of the
        links or sites. Such links/pages may ask for your name, e-mail
        address, phone number etc. The information furnished by you is used
        to provide relevant products and services and to acknowledge
        receipt of your communication or to send out information and
        updates to you. You have option of requesting removal from our
        mailing list. We do not give away your personal information to any
        third party.
      </p>

      <h3 class="policy-page__subheading">Security</h3>
      <p class="section-body">
        To ensure security while transferring sensitive information, all the
        ongoing transmissions between client and server are encrypted using
        advanced and standard protocols. We also practice restricted access
        by employees and hold them to high levels of confidentiality.
      </p>

      <h3 class="policy-page__subheading">Use of cookies</h3>
      <p class="section-body">
        We may use cookies for security, session continuity, and
        customization purposes. In case of a user opting to reject a
        cookie, he/she may not be able to gain access to some of the
        limited services or use some features of the site.
      </p>

      <p class="section-body policy-page__copyright">&copy; 2026 Axon Developers.</p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />

  <style>
    .policy-page {
      padding-top: 5.5rem;
    }

    .policy-page__inner {
      max-width: 640px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .policy-page__heading {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .policy-page__subheading {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-top: 1.25rem;
    }

    .policy-page__copyright {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      opacity: 0.6;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
